{"tid":1050823,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"2019年，仲有冇人有聽Stephy嘅歌？","createTime":"2019-03-07T06:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T11:59:03.000Z","uid":69169,"like":76,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"08f17433993019881f9bcb4dcca88653c4631385","tid":1050823,"uid":69169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:47:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">留在彼此的身邊 牽著手再繼續飛</span></strong><br />\n近排聽返Stephy嘅歌 好多回憶返哂嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://d2xosoyzehxi5w.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/7-alex-fong-stephy-tang.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2xosoyzehxi5w.cloudfront.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F11%2F7-alex-fong-stephy-tang.jpg&h=659e8cde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n愛情大導演葉念琛（👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻😭😭😭😭）執導嘅電影主題曲，膾炙人口嘅合唱歌《十分愛》《七年》《我的最愛》都係唱K必唱嘅經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FWnonD3cqL0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFWnonD3cqL0&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=338d07be\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FWnonD3cqL0</a><br />\n<br />\nmk小小嘅情歌有《藍鞋子》《不要離我太遠》《他不准我哭》；而一d普通嘅情歌又有《再見不是朋友》《日久生情》《分手的禮貌》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eyMDHvDaSeo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeyMDHvDaSeo&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=6f2b3635\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eyMDHvDaSeo</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，亦有一d玩中國風或者唔港式嘅歌︰《七夕》《童謠》《京都之雪》<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7TwnCRSshWQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7TwnCRSshWQ&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=52e91b44\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7TwnCRSshWQ</a><br />\n<br />\n輕鬆d風格又有《青山散步》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kBiypTBdWkM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkBiypTBdWkM&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=050966b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kBiypTBdWkM</a><br />\n<br />\nStephy巔峰時期一定係2007年，不但有《電燈膽》，亦都有連小學生都識唱嘅跑Online主題曲《Fantasy Tale》。但巔峰之時亦都係佢跌落谷底嘅時候，自從走音之後歌唱事業就走下波<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l-1c6xObGcA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dl-1c6xObGcA&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=50129472\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l-1c6xObGcA</a><br />\n<br />\n見到Stephy依家終於唔止係拍葉大導嘅戲，唔洗再做呀寶，戲路多咗，拍《空手道》《藍天白雲》。<img src=\"https://www.cosmopolitan.com.hk/var/cosmopolitanhk/storage/nodejs/files/2017/10/02/15edc213-be19-483e-8d32-a9a114207683.15edc213-be12-4af4-ac57-ccd31ade69a8_708x708.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosmopolitan.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fcosmopolitanhk%2Fstorage%2Fnodejs%2Ffiles%2F2017%2F10%2F02%2F15edc213-be19-483e-8d32-a9a114207683.15edc213-be12-4af4-ac57-ccd31ade69a8_708x708.png&h=32224768&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nStephy唱歌走音唔穩係不爭嘅事實，睇返2018年佢d live都只係比以前好d，無咁震，但都好想佢出返d廣東歌。Stephy幾時出返歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LlnZ9MF9uV4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLlnZ9MF9uV4&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=47e6f628\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LlnZ9MF9uV4</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">憑著極速的腳步 懷內蜜意也找到 全部事蹟都記住</span></strong>"},{"pid":"a81b8655fdd5c70b0417321cd390eb7d736cebc7","tid":1050823,"uid":157197,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:53:05.000Z","msg":"識聽一定係聽我未願意日久生情再見不是朋友"},{"pid":"ec79abc1677828322bd1d38d5ce5336e34c8a878","tid":1050823,"uid":48143,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:54:09.000Z","msg":"以前一路玩online game一路聽<br />\n隻隻入曬腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4c1fc283c843e2c411fcc419115b14a9bf0524","tid":1050823,"uid":136186,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:55:25.000Z","msg":"他不准我哭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590ef28fd20bccbfbcca06404558d612c4da1fbc","tid":1050823,"uid":203657,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:56:38.000Z","msg":"不要離我太遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bda1d821f81ee96bec4a793ee56271a27a6a87c","tid":1050823,"uid":110,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:56:59.000Z","msg":"不速之約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n細個好鐘意聽被遺棄的公主 開頭d音樂好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a58338b2416bd98852f50ae25221f0563b891e7","tid":1050823,"uid":43966,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:59:50.000Z","msg":"陪著我走 日9生情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係百聽不厭"},{"pid":"47e9abdd686a4c2b9cd53183886bc103bd16b2ea","tid":1050823,"uid":120972,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T07:03:09.000Z","msg":"聽開 你好嗎"},{"pid":"73d6b2e3405286ef83425660fa94302839a7153e","tid":1050823,"uid":202553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T07:04:08.000Z","msg":"應承大家 幾時?"},{"pid":"39ba5ab62c0ab4b0b5a77d26bafd5cd701beb4e6","tid":1050823,"uid":85116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0